    "attributes": {
        "action": "Install fences and barriers on bridges over motorways to help prevent suicide",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Suicides or attempted suicides can create traffic chaos, which can then create more mental health issues. Install fences to keep people from attempting suicide from  motorway bridges.",
